description: $20K PRICE REDUCTION!! -MOTIVATED SELLER. Sleek, stylish, and fully renovated, this ground-floor condo in the highly sought-after Mission Plaza community offers modern design and everyday convenience in one perfect package. Step inside to a bright, open-concept layout featuring fresh paint, new flooring throughout, recessed lighting, and clean contemporary lines that create a welcoming and functional space.  The remodeled kitchen is a standout with updated cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and plenty of counter space, ideal for cooking, entertaining, or simply enjoying your morning routine. Both bathrooms have been completely transformed with spa-like finishes, while the bedrooms offer peaceful retreats with generous closet space and natural light.  Enjoy your own private patio, perfect for sipping coffee in the morning or unwinding in the evening. Additional features include a covered carport with storage, a private storage room, and convenient access to the community laundry area.  Mission Plaza provides resort-style amenities including swimming pools, tennis courts, a fitness center, clubhouse, dog run, and BBQ areas, all just steps from your front door. Located in the heart of Mission Valley, this home is minutes from the Trolley Station, Snapdragon Stadium, premier shopping, dining, and major freeways.
